    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Liz Truss announces four new non-executive board members
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The new non-executive board members bring a wealth of experience to the Department to support the delivery of its ambitious trade agenda.
 
</p>

  </div>
</div>

